" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 487px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Shown is a diagrammatic representation of a venous flow velocity waveform",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 467px; height: 318px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The triphasic waveform (S: systole, D: diastole, a: atrial contraction) reflects volume flow changes during the cardiac cycle. The fourth phase is the v-descent, corresponding to the period of end of ventricular systole just before the atrioventricular valves open.",
